      "content": "i mean i know i should ask the doc but i'm actually pretty hungry now and don't want to wait for an appointment. like, i've heard grapefruit is super healthy for your heart anyway. is it really that big of a deal if i just have one glass today? it's not like i'm taking a whole bottle of it.",
