      "content": "it just seems like a lot of worry for one juice. i take my pill in the morning and i'm usually fine, i haven't had any problems yet. if i just wait a few hours after taking the med before i drink the juice, wouldn't that solve the enzyme thing? i really don't want to skip my healthy breakfast.",
